{"tid":247784,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"今天我，去咗天耀廣場（擴建部份）","createTime":"2017-05-18T05:31:59.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-27T03:46:38.000Z","uid":23707,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a51d7da2925f9e55be9c1249cbe907f9f749c765","tid":247784,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T05:31:59.000Z","msg":"前排知道天水圍天耀商場擴建部份改建完開返<br />\n咁就專登入去行下 前身係天耀街市<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實仲未完全開哂 (呢度好似係吉野家)<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/nalj2xmw\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fnalj2xmw&h=7cda0e4b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n新開KFC<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/v9al0gm4\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fv9al0gm4&h=19b2551d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n走廊<br />\n大部份舖頭都未開<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/t24xi1mb\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Ft24xi1mb&h=fbf63b33&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n之前係樓上既138鞋舖<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/3kimu2nf\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F3kimu2nf&h=18ea6a20&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n唯一喜訊: 有吉野家<br />\n仲有無人收購既米線<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/vci4ae5y\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fvci4ae5y&h=23e84e15&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n擴建冷氣部份尾段<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/yiwtc861\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fyiwtc861&h=d4227116&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n另一邊電梯 新開一間OK<br />\n遲D仲有日本餐廳係呢個位<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/50h2r7mu\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F50h2r7mu&h=bab00569&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n改建完留低既<br />\n得返兩邊紅磚牆<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/yk4jf3gd\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fyk4jf3gd&h=9fa67b7f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nBTW領賤食撚屎"},{"pid":"ed2c91